data.text:
Original UK Quad poster for the 1961 Gottfried Reinhardt German/Swiss/U.S. military wartime courtroom lawyer legal crime rape drama.

Film Category: Drama

Actor / Actresses: Kirk Douglas, E.G. Marshall, Christine Kaufmann

Poster Type: UK Quad 30" x 40"

Condition: Good folded condition, censored - swimsuit drawn over, x rating drawn over, general signs of use, such as slight edge and fold wear, minor creases, small tears, pinholes, and smudges, paper loss on border
